msgid "此外，软件还支持 DIP 焊点框、桥接框、焊盘沾胶框、颜色检测框、条形码框等；各类框的检测参数详见 :ref:`检测工具参考`。"
msgstr "The software also provides DIP solder, bridge, glue-on-pad, color, and barcode boxes, among others; for each box's detection parameters, see :ref:`检测工具参考`."
